description: Stunning 1 Bed, 1 Bath, w/ 1 Garage parking space! Boasting 812 square feet of thoughtfully designed living space, this modern home offers a perfect blend of comfort and style. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by an open-concept layout that seamlessly integrates the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating an inviting space for relaxation and entertainment w/ high ceilings and large windows. Kitchen features sleek white shaker style cabinets, quartz countertops, SS appliances, and a breakfast bar for 4 people. The large bedroom offers ample natural light plus a walk in closet. Bathroom is oversized with a dual vanity, quartz countertops and white subway tile. Central AC and Heating, in-unit washer/dryer, beautiful hardwood floors, this modern home has all the amenities one is looking for. Located in the heart of South Boston, minutes to the W Broadway Red Line T stop, the Seaport, South End, and Bar Volpe right at your doorstep. Make this stylish condo your new home today!
